Design an Interactive Tic-Tac-Toe Game in Python
Objective:
Build a two-player (X and O) tic-tac-toe game that allows users to take turns placing their symbols on a 3x3 grid.

Board Class:
There will be methods for : 1. display_board 2. place a marker 3. check winner 4. check if it is a draw 5. check if a position in the board is free to place a marker

Game Class: - play game - switch player
